[Migr-ai-tion.net]Â is
an applied, interdisciplinary
research project that investiga-
tes the potentials of AI as a partici-
patory and therapeutic medium to work with

onialism, stereotypes, margina-
lisation, collective trauma
and agency.

The platform will collect and
